<i>Thanks for paying for me,</i>
<i>Steve, but that doesn't mean</i>

23:26.071 --> 23:27.781
this is a date, does it?
No, no.

23:27.864 --> 23:28.990
But it does mean you
have to dance with me.

23:29.074 --> 23:29.783
